tyle=\"font-weight: 400;\">The perfect excuse to<\/span><b> embark on responsible and cultural tourism<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, to take the trip of a lifetime with someone special, and to enjoy new experiences in an increasingly small world that is full of incredible places to visit.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23596\" title=\"Imagenes blog-01-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-01-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1585\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It doesn&#8217;t matter if you plan it in advance or you like to <\/span><b>travel at the last minute<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The question is not to ignore your curiosity and a desire to explore the planet. <\/span><b>Travelling at the last minute<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> has a high degree of spontaneity and <\/span><b>a good dose of adrenaline.<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> It can also often mean <\/span><b>saving on costs<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And if the main aim of your trip is to rest, why not <\/span><b>travel all inclusive<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. You will enjoy <\/span><b>a unique, relaxing and peaceful experience<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> by booking a package including everything you need for your trip: plane tickets, transfers, accommodation, meals, drinks, leisure, etc. It is also a good way to get <\/span><b>cheap travel<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to destinations with plenty for tourists to see and do.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How do you choose your next destination?<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23604\" title=\"Imagenes blog-02-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-02-min-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-02-min-1.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-02-min-1-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-02-min-1-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-02-min-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-02-min-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-02-min-1-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you are still not sure where to go next, don\u2019t worry. <\/span><b>There are so many places to visit and discover<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. There are some people who narrow down their options to three or four and make a decision from there.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The first and most important question is to <\/span><b>work out which destination you most want to visit<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Then have a look at your budget for the trip. If you don\u2019t know what the trip will cost you, you can search for information on the Internet, and even <\/span><b>make an example flight and hotel booking that will give you a fairly good idea of what it will cost<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23606\" title=\"Imagenes blog-03-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-03-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-03-min-2.jpg 2500w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-03-min-2-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-03-min-2-900x507.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-03-min-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-03-min-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-03-min-2-2048x1153.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another thing to consider is the type of trip you want. Travelling to explore, adventure or relax? Also, think about the activities you want to do, the weather you would like and very importantly, the amount of time you have available for your trip. This will help you to <\/span><b>narrow down the destinations that fit your budget<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Central America: an essential destination in 2020<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Central America is a region where you will find everything you are looking for <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">on your holiday. This is a destination with <\/span><b>an incredible variety of things to do<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, a place where all your dreams can come true.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23598\" title=\"Imagenes blog-04-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-04-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-04-min-2.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-04-min-2-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-04-min-2-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-04-min-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-04-min-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-04-min-2-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You will have the chance to <\/span><b>enjoy the beauty of nature at its best<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, including the impressive biodiversity. It is the perfect place to <\/span><b>enjoy dream beaches in unique natural environments<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and take part in water sports. A paradise with unique architecture and an amazing historical legacy.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you know where to go in Central America?<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are countless <\/span><b>places to visit in<\/b> <a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/centro-america\/recomendaciones-para-viajar\"><b>Central America<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. It is a region with<\/span><b> special countries like Costa Rica, Panama, Nicaragua and Guatemala. <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They are full of traditions, colour and stunning natural beauty.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23600\" title=\"Imagenes blog-05-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-05-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1408\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-05-min-2.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-05-min-2-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-05-min-2-900x507.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-05-min-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-05-min-2-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-05-min-2-2048x1153.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>Guatemala is a favourite destination for travellers from all over the world<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This is a country where you can enjoy beautiful natural landscapes like the Pacaya and San Pedro volcanoes and the black beaches of Itzapa. You can also <\/span><b>admire the indigenous and colonial vestiges<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> scattered throughout the country.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/guatemala\/paquetes\/triangulo-maya-guatemala-el-salvador-y-honduras\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Honduras<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/visita-nicaragua\/tours-de-un-dia\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nicaragua<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and El Salvador are some other <\/span><b>Central American countries that are worth visiting.<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> True <\/span><b>natural jewels<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> offering unique experiences in <\/span><b>extremely beautiful natural spaces<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that hide impressive <\/span><b>archaeological treasures<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that will take you back to ancient times and fascinating civilisations, passing through the colonial period, to the region\u2019s intense contemporary history.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23602\" title=\"Imagenes blog-06-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-06-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-06-min-3.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-06-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-06-min-3-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-06-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-06-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-06-min-3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Costa Rica is, without a doubt, somewhere you must visit during <\/span><b>your trip to Central America<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Its natural parks full of life and colour will be in your memories forever. And in Panama, as well as enjoying a unique cosmopolitan city, you can also see its famous canal in action. That is one of the things that makes it an unmissable destination in this region.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>When is the best time to travel to Central America?<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can visit <\/span><b>Central America<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> throughout the year because the region generally <\/span><b>enjoys a very pleasant climate for visitors.<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Although there are differences between the different areas, in general, it has a <\/span><b>tropical, humid and warm climate<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This is what has brought about its amazing natural wealth.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23608\" title=\"Imagenes blog-07-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-07-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-07-min-3.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-07-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-07-min-3-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-07-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-07-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-07-min-3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before planning <\/span><b>trips to Central America, <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">you should find out about the weather in the specific region you want to visit because there are <\/span><b>many diverse microclimates<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The most mountainous areas, lying at more than 2,500 metres above sea level, are where you will find the lowest temperatures. However, in the low areas, temperatures are warm and can reach up to 27 degrees throughout the year.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In spite of this, <\/span><b>there are two noticeable seasons: the wet and the dry season, <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">determined by the volume of rainfall. The wet or rainy season runs from May to November; and the dry season is from December to April.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23610\" title=\"Imagenes blog-09-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-09-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-09-min-3.jpg 2500w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-09-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-09-min-3-900x507.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-09-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-09-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-09-min-3-2048x1153.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>The best time to travel to Central America is whenever you decide<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> depending on your expectations and the activities you plan to do. The rains are not especially heavy so they will not spoil your trip. For example, if you want to surf, depending on the region you travel to (north, south or central Pacific) the best months will be from December to April (north) or from April to September (south).<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Places you can&#8217;t miss in Central America<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although there are countless <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/centro-america\/lugares-exoticos-para-viajar-en-centro-america\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">places<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to visit and things to do in Central America, here are some of the ones we consider <\/span><b>essential to get the flavour of a region where there is still so much to discover<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/guatemala\/tours\/excursion-a-tikal\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tikal National Park in Guatemala<\/span><\/a><\/h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23612\" title=\"Imagenes blog-08-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-08-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-08-min-3.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-08-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-08-min-3-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-08-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-08-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-08-min-3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A true <\/span><b>archaeological jewel<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that will give you an insight into the <\/span><b>mysteries of the pre-Columbian Mayan civilisation<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Be sure to visit the aerial viewpoint above Temple IV on the west side of the park.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/costa-rica\/actividades-en-tu-viaje-al-volcan-arenal\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Arenal Volcano in Costa Rica<\/span><\/a><\/h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23616\" title=\"Imagenes blog-11-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-11-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-11-min-3.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-11-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-11-min-3-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-11-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-11-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-11-min-3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>One of the most majestic active volcanoes in the world<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> located in the Arenal Volcano National Park. One of the park\u2019s main attractions is to take the <\/span><b>old lava trail formed in 1992<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> while enjoying the spectacular views of the park\u2019s main sights: the Arenal volcano, the Arenal lake and the Chato volcano.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/panama\/canal-de-panama-7-cosas-que-debes-saber-antes-de-visitarlo\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Panama Canal<\/span><\/a><\/h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23618\" title=\"Imagenes blog-12-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-12-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-12-min-3.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-12-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-12-min-3-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-12-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-12-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-12-min-3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">An impressive <\/span><b>engineering masterpiece<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that connects around 144 sea routes. From the Miraflores locks you can admire the full magnitude of this complex <\/span><b>system of water lifts<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that 35 to 40 ships pass through every day.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/centro-america\/10-destinos-en-honduras\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Roatan Island in Honduras<\/span><\/a><\/h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23620\" title=\"Imagenes blog-13-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-13-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-13-min-3.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-13-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-13-min-3-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-13-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-13-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-13-min-3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>A tropical paradise perfect for diving and snorkelling<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Turquoise waters, fine sand and the second largest coral reef in the world are only part of what this incredible island has to offer. Its waters <\/span><b>are home to over 70 species of stony corals<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, 350 species of molluscs and one of the largest manatee populations on the planet.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><a href=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/panama\/tours\/pasea-la-historia-panama-la-ciudad-casco-antiguo\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Panama old town<\/span><\/a><\/h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23622\" title=\"Imagenes blog-14-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-14-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-14-min-3.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-14-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-14-min-3-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-14-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-14-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-14-min-3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>Unmissable for history lovers<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The perfect place to discover and appreciate the history and architecture of the colonial era. A<\/span><b> Unesco World Heritage Site since 1997<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> where you can visit famous buildings like the Church of San Jos\u00e9, the Plaza Mayor, the Jesuit Convent and the Municipal Palace.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Travel recommendations for Central America<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now that you know a little about Central America, you can add it to your dream destinations for 2020. But before travelling, remember the following recommendations:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Before travelling, <\/span><b>find out about mandatory and recommended vaccines<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for each country. One of the most important of which is for yellow fever. Also ask about the <\/span><b>recommended chemoprophylaxis to prevent malaria<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23624\" title=\"Imagenes blog-15-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-15-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-15-min-3.jpg 2500w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-15-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-15-min-3-900x507.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-15-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-15-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-15-min-3-2048x1153.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Remember to pack a full <\/span><b>mosquito protection kit<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: mosquito net, repellents, long-sleeved shirts and long trousers.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; If you go on excursions in the jungle or other natural areas, <\/span><b>never touch a wild animal<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. They might bite and give you an infectious disease.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23626\" title=\"Imagenes blog-16-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-16-min-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-16-min-3.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-16-min-3-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-16-min-3-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-16-min-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-16-min-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-16-min-3-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>&#8211; Always drink bottled water<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. Although some countries like Costa Rica, Honduras and El Salvador promise good water quality, it is better to avoid possible gastroenteritis and other stomach upsets.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Take out <\/span><b>travel insurance with international coverage<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Take a <\/span><b>small first-aid kit<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> with everything you need for first aid, including antidiarrheals and pain relief.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23628\" title=\"Imagenes blog-17-min\" src=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-17-min-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2501\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-17-min-2.jpg 2501w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-17-min-2-510x287.jpg 510w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-17-min-2-900x506.jpg 900w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-17-min-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-17-min-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/Imagenes-blog-17-min-2-2048x1152.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2501px) 100vw, 2501px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Take <\/span><b>summer clothes,<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> but include some warmer items: the temperatures are usually a little cooler at night.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Don&#8217;t forget <\/span><b>sunscreen<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.asuaire.com\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you have decided to<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"http:\/\/www.asuaire.com\/\"><b>travel a lot<\/b><\/a> <a href=\"http:\/\/www.asuaire.com\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">in 2020<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, <\/span><b>Central America is one of the best destinations<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> you could imagine. You can enjoy unique experiences in a special location full of natural wealth. <\/span><b>The perfect place to make all your travel dreams come true <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">this year.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":23596,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"content-type":"","footnotes":""},"categories":[870],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-23088","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-central-america","infinite-scroll-item","generate-columns","tablet-grid-50","mobile-grid-100","grid-parent","grid-25","no-featured-image-padding"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23088","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=23088"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23088\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":23632,"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/23088\/revisions\/23632"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/23596"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=23088"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=23088"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/asuaire.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=23088"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}